{
  "$comment": [
    "Cron jobs auth: lib/cron-auth.ts accepts EITHER `x-vercel-cron: 1`",
    "(set automatically by Vercel's scheduler) OR `Authorization: Bearer",
    "$CRON_SECRET`. Vercel's automatic cron works without CRON_SECRET,",
    "but external triggers (curl, GitHub Actions) require it. Set",
    "CRON_SECRET in the Vercel project's Environment Variables page",
    "(Production + Preview + Development). Generate a value with:",
    "  openssl rand -hex 32",
    "Vercel's JSON parser ignores $comment fields."
  ],
